OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSolve worker shortages with
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fimmigration - CBI boss     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK should use immigration to solve 
OL,6, worker shortages and boost economic    
OL,7, growth, the boss of the UK's biggest   
OL,8, business group will say on Monday.     
OL,10,FTony Danker will call on politicians to
OL,11,Fbe "practical" about immigration at the
OL,12,FCBI's conference in Birmingham.        
OL,14,FMr Danker will also say the UK should  
OL,15,Fenable "economic migration" in areas   
OL,16,Fwhere skilled workers cannot be found. 
OL,18,FHis speech comes as many firms struggle
OL,19,Fto recruit staff, with job vacancies   
OL,20,Fnear record levels.                    
